# Contributing to Adaptive Adoption

Thanks for your interest.

## Principles
- Operational over aspirational
- Evidence-aware (cite primary sources when possible)
- Fork-friendly (assume industry extensions)
- Safety-first (prefer evaluation, guardrails, and review)

## Where to contribute
- `docs/pillars/` (pillar narratives)
- `docs/theory/` (foundations + sources)
- `diagnostics/` (assessment instruments)
- `tools/` (playbooks + templates)
- `industry-modules/` (domain extensions)
